[normal]2 [bold]About Thompsons[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Thompsons Solicitors has been standing up for the injured and mistreated since the firm was founded by Harry Thompson in 1921. We have fought for millions of people, won countless landmark cases and secured key legal reforms. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]We have more experience of w
[normal]inning personal injury and employment claims than any other firm – and we use that experience solely for the injured and mistreated.
[normal] 
[normal]We do not work for insurance companies or employers
[normal],
[normal] a
[normal]nd we have 
[normal]never taken 
[normal]part in the merry-go-round of referrals betwee
[normal]n the insurance industry, claims companies and some lawyers
[normal].
