[normal]’
[normal]. In
[normal] 
[normal]the first nine months of 2013, Direct Line 
[normal]released a further 
[normal]£311.1 million
[normal] from reserves and said: “
[normal]The bulk of the release arose in the Motor division where the Group has experienced favourable development on bodily injury claims, which is currently expected to continue
[normal]”
